        public SleepData(int cali_flag,
                 int sleepQulity,
                 int wakeCount,
                 int deepSleepTime,
                 int lowSleepTime,
                 int allSleepTime,
                 java.lang.String sleepLine,
                 TimeData sleepDown,
                 TimeData sleepUp)
        Sleep data
        parameters:
        cali_flag - Sleep calibration value, this value is currently useless
        sleepQulity - Sleep Quality
        wakeCount - Number of waking ups during sleep
        deepSleepTime - Duration of Deep Sleep
        lowSleepTime - Light Sleep Duration
        allSleepTime - Total Sleep Time
        sleepLine - Get sleep curve, mainly used for more iconicUIto display sleep status (refer to our companyAPP,360Application Market SearchHband) if you sleep the interface toUINo special requirements, ignore,Sleep curve is divided into ordinary sleep and precision sleep, ordinary sleep is a group of0,1,2A string of characters, each character representing the duration is5minutes of which0means light sleep,1means deep sleep,2means wake,such as "201112"with length6, indicating a total of sleep stages30minutes, head and tail awake5minutes with light sleep5minutes, deep sleep15minutes;For precise sleep, the sleep curve is a set of0,1,2,3,4A string of characters, each character representing the duration is1minutes of which0means deep sleep,1means light sleep,2for rapid eye movement,3indicates insomnia,4means wake up.
        sleepDown - Sleep time
        sleepUp - Wake Up Time
